-- Turkey's Halkbank bids for majority stake in Serbian lender Cacanska
-- By Ayla Jean Yackley
-- Fri Aug 15, 2014 01:37AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Aug 15 (Reuters) - Turkey's state-run lender Halkbank <HALKB.IS> said on Friday it has offer to buy a 76.76 percent stake in Serbian lender Cacanska Banka <CCNB.BEL> for an undisclosed sum.

